</td>
<td class="mbox-text" style=""><b>Please help <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Quebec_French&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Quebec_French&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">improve this section</a> by expanding it.</b> Further information might be found on the <a href="/wiki/Talk:Quebec_French" title="Talk:Quebec French">talk page</a>. <small><i>(June 2008)</i></small></td>
